net.openhft.chronicle.bytes

Class MappedFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.openhft.chronicle.bytes.MappedFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.openhft.chronicle.core.ReferenceCounted

    public class MappedFile
extends Object
implements net.openhft.chronicle.core.ReferenceCounted
    A memory mapped files which can be randomly accessed in chunks. It has overlapping regions to avoid wasting bytes at the end of chunks.
